%S A393739 1,1,4,14,85,598,4837,41570,372815,3435968,32368180,310322386
%N A393739 Number of free polyominoes in the {8,3} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%H A393739 Ed Wynn, <a href="/A393739/a393739_1.c.txt">C program for A393739(n) and several other sequences</a>
%F A393739 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q; also P{p,q}(q+1) = P{p,oo}(q+1) + floor((p-1)/2) - floor((3+q(p-2))/2). In this case, p=8, q=3 and P{p,oo} = A389937.
%o A393739 (C) // See Wynn link.
%Y A393739 Cf. A259353, A393740, A393741, A393742, A393743, A393744, A389937.
